name: function.name
description: Function name shim (especially for supporting function names in Internet Explorer).
author: Ionică Bizău <bizauionica@gmail.com> (https://ionicabizau.net)

blah.description: If the name field is not accessible (usually this happens on Internet Explorer), it will be defined.
blah.documentation: Usually, you will **not** use this as function but you will access the `name` field on the function directly.
